quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  26,123,Aad denied the messengers
  26,124,"When/if their brother Hood said to them: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  26,125,That I am for you a faithful messenger
  26,126,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,127,"And I do not ask/beg you on it from a wage/fee/reward, that truly my wage/reward (is) except on the creations all together`s/(universe`s) Lord"
  26,128,"Do you build/construct at every/each high hill an evidence , something useless in vanity"
  26,129,"And you take factories , maybe/perhaps you be immortal/eternal"
  26,130,"And if you destroyed/attacked violently, you destroyed/attacked violently (as) tyrants/rebels"
  26,131,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,132,And fear and obey who extended/spread you with what you know
  26,133,He extended/spread you with camels/livestock and sons/sons and daughters
  26,134,And treed gardens/paradises and water springs/wells
  26,135,That I fear on (for) you a great day`s` torture
  26,136,"They said: \"(It is) equal/alike on (to) us, had you preached/advised , or you did not be from the preachers/advisers"
  26,137,That truly that (is) except the first`s/beginner`s nature/character
  26,138,And we are not with being tortured
  26,139,"So they denied him , so We made them die/destroyed them, that truly in that (is) an evidence/sign (E), and most of them were not believing"
  26,140,"And that truly your Lord He is (E), the glorious/mighty , the merciful"